PrecisEnactment of the XIII PAN AMERICAN GAMES REMISSION ORDER - which provides for the remission of customs duties, excise taxes and some or all of the GST payable on various kinds of goods imported in connection with the XIII Pan American Games to be held in Winnipeg from July 23 to August 8, 1999.
